    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Courts in Great Britain and in some American states that administer specifically the law of equity and proceed according to the forms and principles of equity, as opposed to the common law or statutory law.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Úsese para cortes en Gran Bretaña y algunos estados americanos que administran específicamente la ley de equidad y proceden de acuerdo a las formas y principios de equidad, contrariamente a la ley común o derecho estatuario.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Te gebruiken voor rechtbanken in Groot-Brittannië en enkele Amerikaanse staten die zich specifiek bezighouden met het 'equity-recht' en werken volgens de vormen en beginselen van equity, in tegenstelling tot het gewoonterecht ('common law’) of wettelijk recht 'statutory law'.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指英國以及某些美國州內所設立的法院。衡平法院專司衡平法，並依據衡平法的慣例與原則進行判決，而非普通法或成文法。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
